    A Google Compute Engine Subnetwork. Subnetworks segments your cloud network IP space into subnetworks. Subnetwork prefixes can be automatically allocated, or you can create a custom topology. Objects of this class are immutable. To get a Subnetwork object with the most recent information use reload(com.google.cloud.compute.Compute.SubnetworkOption...).
